name: V I S I O N S

metadata.name: D I S S O N A N C E / /
metadata.description:
A fractured state of mind. Surely, I'm close to the answers I seek?

Why else would I be here, picking up the fragments piece by piece.

The time for rest will surely come, only then will I close my eyes. 

Until then I press forward, to absolve the dissonance of my mind.
